@startuml
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam diagramBorderColor transparent
skinparam diagramBorderThickness 0

skinparam participant {
  BorderColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #eeeeee
  FontSize 13
  FontColor #333333
  Padding 8
}

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  ArrowThickness 1.5
  LifeLineBorderColor #bbbbbb
  ArrowFontSize 11
  ArrowFontColor #444444
}

participant "오케스트레이터" as Orch
participant "상품" as P
participant "배달" as D
participant "주문" as O

Orch -> P: ① 재고 차감
P --> Orch: ② 성공

Orch -> D: ③ 배달 생성
D --> Orch: ④ 실패

Orch -[#cc0000]> P: ⑤ 재고 원복 (자동 롤백)
Orch -[#cc0000]> O: ⑥ 주문 취소

@enduml
